          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2019-02-08T22:42:12Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Iran Human Rights Accountability Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Comprehensive Iran Sanctions, Accountability, and Divestment Act of 2010 with respect to the list of sanctionable Iranian government officials or persons acting on behalf of such government who are responsible for or complicit in certain human rights abuses to include as sanctionable activities human rights abuses committed against U.S. citizens or legal permanent resident aliens. </p>]]></text>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2018-03-19</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2018-03-19T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
    </summaries>
    <congress>115</congress>
    <titles>
      <item>
        <title>To provide for the imposition of sanctions on persons who are officials of the Government of Iran or persons acting on behalf of that Government who are responsible for or complicit in human rights abuses committed against citizens of the United States or United States legal permanent resident aliens.</title>
